<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:larger;"><strong>Articles referenced in this tale:</strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2422">SCP-2422</a> <span style="font-size:smaller;">by OverThinking</span><br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2240">SCP-2240</a> <span style="font-size:smaller;">by Mdnthrvst</span><br />
