<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-076">SCP-076</a> <span style="font-size:smaller;">by Kain Pathos Crow</span><br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-073">SCP-073</a> <span style="font-size:smaller;">by Kain Pathos Crow</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:larger;"><strong>Backstory:</strong></span></p>
<p>SCP-2422 was created by a mysterious entity known as Wandering Father, created to exist within Site-17 and bring Joy to its occupants. Not much else is known about their past.</p>
<p>These few classified interview logs – passed down to an incoming Project Director by his predecessor – reveal their origins and their story through their interactions with each other, their containment, and the various researchers who work with them.</p>
<p>There is always more than meets the eye.</p>
</blockquote>
